{"tid":717624,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]屋企有1000M光纖，用WiFi+MBA，上網好慢","createTime":"2018-06-26T07:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T06:47:01.000Z","uid":31305,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"743a054d11be129a2b55f53faa2d9a478c664749","tid":717624,"uid":31305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"屋企裝左1000M光纖上網好耐，<br />\n平時睇下連登fb ig都冇問題嘅，<br />\n但一要睇片 無論online定下載都好慢，AV疾疾下好不爽<br />\nSpeedtest通常得3-4MB/s<br />\n想救問下有咩方法解決？<br />\n<br />\n我估應該要換過個router？我果個都用左兩年<br />\n有冇話買router要注意D咩?<br />\n<br />\n另外有聽人講本身用MacBook air上網已經慢一截，關唔關事？有冇方法改善<br />\n<br />\n謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975799864c2981ce0af923f74ffcfb2bb96ee305","tid":717624,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:40:04.000Z","msg":"router咩型號又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9372a7cf51ea0ca49fe4962d9bc9c3e05072c1f3","tid":717624,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"mba咁垃圾都用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863a3c39f385319b9d4b5ba55dfae7e70c675042","tid":717624,"uid":31305,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"975799864c2981ce0af923f74ffcfb2bb96ee305","tid":717624,"uid":6164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:40:04.000Z","msg":"router咩型號又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"TP Link AC1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b838541cb9d38fe13ff1befc61b56eb2c36f6619","tid":717624,"uid":31305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9372a7cf51ea0ca49fe4962d9bc9c3e05072c1f3","tid":717624,"uid":619