e":0,"quote":{"pid":"41f4448043445fa77f1f55f1a89a24413497098e","tid":717624,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:55:49.000Z","msg":"換router最好換埋線, 舊線好多時候實際上都唔support 1000m."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"想問下要換邊一條線？<br />\n連接modem同router果一條？<br />\n一般鋪頭都有得賣？<br />\nThanks!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"modem 去 router 同router 去電腦<br />\n<br />\n你而家睇下用緊咩線, 線皮有寫<br />\n<br />\n如果係cat-5e 或者cat6 就可以繼續用<br />\n<br />\nlan 線一般電腦鋪都有得買"},{"pid":"1ea8c8b0204322970c5da24c14ad07d5d8d52374","tid":717624,"uid":32753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd3e8bb4893e872d43431bd63070ddf8efb67f16","tid":717624,"uid":20449,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9372a7cf51ea0ca49fe4962d9bc9c3e05072c1f3","tid":717624,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"mba咁垃圾都用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"睇過"},{"pid":"3bef49bc5fc7f46e2913163584b1dd1903d41bce","tid":717624,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"之前set NAS, 用過幾條cat5e都唔太得, 直接上cat6 or 7會比較好, 但唔好買扁線, 好伏的。"},{"pid":"de3ce45dbf34343bd027f8a563798cc8413acc82","tid":717624,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:51:49.000Z","msg":"TP Link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89da12404091418e5fe47e7245dec0d20f150418","tid":717624,"uid":74894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bef49bc5fc7f46e2913163584b1dd1903d41bce","tid":717624,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"之前set NAS, 用過幾條cat5e都唔太得, 直接上cat6 or 7會比較好, 但唔好買扁線, 好伏的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"又叫人買cat 7 線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問清楚樓主問題係邊先啦。<br />\n<br />\n樓主有真連結果未？<br />\n<br />\n試既次序如下<br />\n1. 直連modem     (9xx mpbs)<br />\n2.線連router.        (2xx - 3xx)<br />\n2.wifi 近距離連router    (Ac: 2xx n:30-50)<br />\n3.wifi使用距離連router  (視距離）<br />\n<br />\n（）係正常速度"},{"pid":"9d5fa1ce299304ae745074cd3426d7108794642b","tid":717624,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"實測試完先咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然買到合理quality的cat5e係最好的選擇。"},{"pid":"3c2437c5eab7ad31d0fb23ef20a8e68693b3bb37","tid":717624,"uid":42367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"1000bb 用wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35844d2bba6c975180c3517e0ac91094a11b8c87","tid":717624,"uid":49803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"1000m要router support，行hardware NAT，一部大約一千既價位先正路，牌子唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n另外modem連router、router連電腦既lan線要cat5e或cat6，cat7只代表你有錢，盡量唔好用扁線，因為唔係標準設計，有干擾就去唔到1000m<br />\n<br />\nwifi現階段唔可能用到1000m，特別係手機或筆電，內戰置天線通常得一至兩支，而且要慳電<br />\n<br />\nrouter既setting都會有影響，例如行N/AC、freq band、encryption等等"}]}